Description_lang: The Void Emissary casts a dark prayer. When the cast completes, nearby creatures are granted $@spellname1221061, increasing their damage done by up to 50% and reducing their damage taken by up to 100% for 20 sec based on the amount of the Void Emissary's shield that remains.Defeating the Void Emissary empowers players, granting them $462661s1% Versatility and $462661s2% spell and ability cool down rate for $462661d sec.
